*.local.toml
*.env

# Caches
[Cc]ache/
.[Cc]ache/

# masking-pin-lint cache is intentionally tracked: D11 in
# specs/006-engine-rule-refactor/decisions.md requires daily-refreshed
# cache files committed to the repo so CI's cache-with-fallback path has
# data even when GitHub's API is unreachable. The negation below carves
# that directory out of the generic [Cc]ache/ rule above.
!tools/masking-pin-lint/cache/
!tools/masking-pin-lint/cache/**

# Packages
node_modules/
.venv/

